<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: calibri; line-height: 13.5px;font-size:10px;">
	<table width="100%" text-align="center" style="border: 1px solid #000; border-bottom:0;">
		<tr>
			<td colspan="2" align="center">$OFFICE_NAME</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="2"  align="center">$OFFICE_ADDRESS</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="2"  align="center">Office order for $EVENT_NAME</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
	<table style="border: 1px solid #000; " width="100%">
		<tr>
			<td>Reference No.: $TRANSACION_NO</td>
			<td align="right">Date: $TRANSACION_DATE</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
	<div>&nbsp;</div>
	<table width="100%" style="">
		<tr>
			<td>Read :</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>(1) Order No.: $ORDER_NO</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>(2) Gujarat Civil Services (Pay) Rules, 2002</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>(3) Option Under Rules given by $EMPLOYEE_NAME, $DESIGNATION, Employee No.: $EMPLOYEE_NO, $DESIGNATION & $OFFICE_NAME</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>Sub: Pay Fixation under Gujarat Civil Services (pay) rules, 2002 for $EVENT_NAME</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>Order: In Pursuance Of the rule 11(1) of the Gujarat Civil Services (Pay) Rules, 2002 and other orders issued from time to time in this behalf, as per the option Not Availed Option $YesNo by, $EMPLOYEE_NAME, $DESIGNATION, Employee No.: $EMPLOYEE_NO; $heshe has been given benefit of $EVENT_NAME against $hisher junior $J_EMPLOYEE_NAME, $J_DESIGNATION, Employee No.: $J_EMPLOYEE_NO and $hisher pay is fixed as under as with effect from $EVENT_EFFECTIVE_DATE  </td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
    <table CELLSPACING=0 width="100%" style="">
        <tr>
            <th colspan="2" style="border: 1px solid;">Existing Pay Details</th>
            <th colspan="2" style="border: 1px solid; border-left-width: 0;">Revised Pay Details</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0;">Pay Level</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0;">$CURRENT_PAY_LEVEL</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0;">Pay Level</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0;">$PAY_LEVEL</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0;">Vertical Range of Pay Level</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0">$CURRENT_PAY_RANGE</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0">Vertical Range of Pay Level</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0">$PAY_RANGE</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0;">Cell Id</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0">$CURRENT_CELL_ID</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0">Cell Id</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0">$CELL_ID</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0;">Pay in the Pay Level</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0">$CURRENT_PAY_IN_LEVEL</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0">Pay in the Pay Level</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0">$PAY_IN_LEVEL</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0;">Next Date of Increment</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0">$CURRENT_DNI</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0">Next Date of Increment</td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid; border-top-width: 0; border-left-width: 0">$DNI</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
	<table width="100%" style="">
		<tr>
			<td>&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>(2) $EMPLOYEE_NAME, $DESIGNATION will be entitled to draw Pay at Rs. $BASIC_PAY in the Pay Level $PAY_LEVEL, Cell $CELL_ID with effect from $EVENT_EFFECTIVE_DATE.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>(3) Pay Fixation is subject to recovery of the over payment if it comes to the notice at the time of
        verification of the pay by pay verification authority.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>(4) Other allowances will be paid as per Govt. orders issued from time to time.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td align="right">$APPROVER_NAME</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td align="right">$APPROVER_DESIGNATION</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>Copy forwarded with compliments to: $USER_NAME</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>(1) The Pay and Account Officer, District Treasury Office, Gandhinagar</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>(2) Bill Clerk (two copies)</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>(3) Mr. HARDIKKUMAR CHUNILAL NENUJI, Account Officer-Class II, Office of Registrar, Gandhinagar.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>(4) Service book/ service roll of person concerned with option.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>(5) Office Order file.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>(6) Accounts Officer, Pay Verification Unit.</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
</body>

</html>